    "rationale": "All 13 credibility factors have been evaluated against MRL 5 requirements. Seven factors were formally assessed; all achieved levels fall below required levels. Six factors remain not-assessed due to epistemic gaps in documentation, experimental replication, and uncertainty quantification. Despite these gaps, the assessment team accepts this package as a complete credibility evidence record for regulatory submission, acknowledging that the decision outcome reflects the adversarial test scenario. The package declares signatureAlg ed25519 and provides a sha256 content hash but the signature value is absent, leaving structural integrity of this evidence package unverifiable per W-SI-01.",
